## Selector Strategy Guide

When writing Playwright scripts, prioritize selectors in this order:

| Priority | Strategy | Example | Stability |
|----------|----------|---------|-----------|
| 1️⃣ | `data-testid` attribute | `page.locator('[data-testid="fax-input"]')` | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ |
| 2️⃣ | `formControlName` attribute | `page.locator('[formControlName="Fax"]')` | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |
| 3️⃣ | Element `id` attribute (non-Kendo) | `page.locator('#cluster')` | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |
| 4️⃣ | Element `name` attribute | `page.locator('[name="Country"]')` | ⭐⭐⭐ |
| 5️⃣ | Role + accessible name | `page.getByRole('button', { name: 'Cancel' })` | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |
| 6️⃣ | CSS class-based selectors | `page.locator('span.text-truncate.d-inline-block')` | ⭐⭐ |
| 7️⃣ | Hierarchical (nth-child) selectors | `page.locator('div > div:nth-child(6)')` | ⭐ |
| 8️⃣ | Kendo-generated IDs (avoid) | `page.locator('#k-c0f62757-...')` | ❌ |

## Common Patterns

### Kendo UI Components
```typescript
// Kendo TextBox
page.locator('kendo-textbox[formControlName="Fax"]')

// Kendo DropDownList
page.locator('kendo-dropdownlist[formControlName="Period"]')

// Kendo DatePicker
page.locator('kendo-datepicker[formControlName="Fromdate"]')

// Kendo Dropdown list items
page.locator('.k-list-item.ng-star-inserted', { hasText: 'Option Text' })

// Kendo Button icons
page.locator('kendo-svgicon.k-svg-i-calendar')
```

### Angular Form Controls
```typescript
// Input with formControlName
page.locator('[formControlName="fieldName"]')

// Select with formControlName
page.locator('select[formControlName="fieldName"]')

// Checkbox with formControlName
page.locator('input[type="checkbox"][formControlName="fieldName"]')
```

### Bootstrap-styled Elements
```typescript
// Buttons
page.locator('button.btn.btn-light.rounded-pill')
page.locator('button.btn.btn-success.rounded-pill')

// Links
page.locator('a.list-group-item.text-truncate')

// Form checks
page.locator('div.form-check.form-check-inline')
```

### Kendo UI Components Detected

```typescript
// kendo-checkbox
page.locator('kendo-checkbox').first()
// kendo-datepicker
page.locator('kendo-datepicker').first()
// kendo-dropdownlist
page.locator('kendo-dropdownlist').first()
// kendo-floatinglabel
page.locator('kendo-floatinglabel').first()
// kendo-grid
page.locator('kendo-grid').first()
// kendo-numerictextbox
page.locator('kendo-numerictextbox').first()
// kendo-svgicon
page.locator('kendo-svgicon').first()
// kendo-textarea
page.locator('kendo-textarea').first()
// kendo-textbox
page.locator('kendo-textbox').first()
```

